#

Mint Chocolate Chip Milkshake

5 min
$5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariannut-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

dessertbeveragesweet

Description

A refreshing and indulgent milkshake with the classic flavor of mint and rich chocolate chips.

Ingredients

  • vanilla ice cream: 2 cups
  • milk: 1 cup
  • mint extract: 1/2 teaspoon
  • chocolate chips: 1/4 cup
  • whipped cream (optional): for topping
  • chocolate syrup (optional): for drizzling
